        <trans-unit id="109" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>The focus state occurs when the mouse pointer is hovering over the <ph id="ph1">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Controls.Menu&gt;</ph> and pressed state occurs when a mouse button is clicked over the <ph id="ph2">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Controls.Menu&gt;</ph>.</source>
